            "secId": "sec5",
            "sentence": "So let us consider the case (a) pre-holes.",
            "startOffset": 197771,
            "title": "Preholes in flawless graphs"
        },
        {
            "endOffset": 163561,
            "parents": [],
            "refoffsets": {
                "b6": {
