            "title": "Structure of the paper"
        },
        {
            "endOffset": 168639,
            "parents": [
                {
                    "id": "sec1",
                    "title": "Introduction"
                }
            ],
            "secId": "sec1.2",
            "sentence": "We complete the process by checking for pre-holes, using a procedure given in 5.2.",
            "startOffset": 168557,
            "title": "Structure of the paper"
        },
        {
            "endOffset": 168977,
            "parents": [
                {
                    "id": "sec1",
                    "title": "Introduction"
                }
            ],
            "secId": "sec1.2",
            "sentence": "Section 7 summarises the algorithm with a formal description, and discusses its running time.",
            "startOffset": 168884,
            "title": "Structure of the paper"
        },
        {
            "endOffset": 168182,
            "parents": [
                {
                    "id": "sec1",
                    "title": "Introduction"
                }
            ],
            "secId": "sec1.2",
            "sentence": "We describe how to find such a hole in 3.3.",
            "startOffset": 168139,
            "title": "Structure of the paper"
        },
        {
            "endOffset": 167940,
            "parents": [
                {
                    "id": "sec1",
                    "title": "Introduction"
                }
            ],
            "secId": "sec1.2",
            "sentence": "We begin, in Section 3.1, by proving some properties of quasimonotone graphs for later use, using the characterisation of monotone graphs by forbidden induced subgraphs.",
            "startOffset": 167771,
            "title": "Structure of the paper"
        },
        {
